snippet.title: Stories of Liane Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Several centuries in the future, Earth has been destroyed. Corporations have gone to the stars in search of a new home. These are the stories from this dark era of history. 

Stories of Liane is a first-person experimental experience. It is a collection of short stories that take place during an era of the dying human race. Available on Steam for free March 2021.

Add to your wishlist and learn more here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1524110/Stories_of_Liane/?beta=0

#ue4 #unrealengine #indiegame
